==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Peeler
<hw>Peel"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A nickname for a policeman; -- so
called from <person>Sir Robert <etsep>Peel</etsep></person>.</def>
<mark>[British Slang]</mark> <see>See <er>Bobby</er>.</see>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

